### Data Flow: Template Execution

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API
    participant Scheduler
    participant Executor
    participant AnomalyDetector
    participant AlertManager
    participant Database

    User->>API: POST /schedules (schedule template)
    API->>Scheduler: add_job(template, trigger)
    Scheduler->>Database: Store instance configuration
    Scheduler-->>API: job_id
    API-->>User: Schedule created

    Note over Scheduler: Time trigger fires

    Scheduler->>Executor: execute_template(instance)
    Executor->>Database: Create execution record (status: running)
    Executor->>Executor: Collect metrics from sources
    Executor->>Database: Store metrics

    Executor->>AnomalyDetector: check_anomalies(metrics)
    AnomalyDetector->>AnomalyDetector: Calculate z-scores
    AnomalyDetector-->>Executor: anomalies[]

    Executor->>AlertManager: evaluate_alerts(template, metrics, anomalies)
    AlertManager->>AlertManager: Evaluate alert rules
    AlertManager->>Database: Store alerts
    AlertManager->>Notification Service: Dispatch notifications
    AlertManager-->>Executor: alerts[]

    Executor->>Database: Update execution (status: completed)
    Executor->>Database: Update instance (last_execution, next_execution)
```

