## Configuration

### Environment Variables

#### Required Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Description |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| `DATABASE_URL` | string | PostgreSQL connection string (format: `postgresql://user:pass@host:port/db`) |
| `REDIS_URL` | string | Redis connection string (format: `redis://:password@host:port/db`) |
| `JWT_SECRET_KEY` | string | JWT signing secret (minimum 32 characters, must match auth-service) |

#### Service Configuration

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `SERVICE_NAME` | `osint-service` | Service identifier |
| `SERVICE_PORT` | `8004` | HTTP server port |
| `DEBUG` | `false` | Enable debug mode (auto-reload, verbose logging) |

#### Database Configuration

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `DATABASE_POOL_SIZE` | `20` | Maximum database connections in pool |
| `DATABASE_MAX_OVERFLOW` | `10` | Maximum overflow connections beyond pool size |
| `DATABASE_ECHO` | `false` | Log all SQL queries (use for debugging) |

#### Redis Configuration

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `REDIS_CACHE_TTL` | `3600` | Default cache TTL in seconds (1 hour) |

#### Scheduler Configuration

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `SCHEDULER_ENABLED` | `true` | Enable APScheduler (set to false to disable scheduling) |
| `SCHEDULER_MAX_INSTANCES` | `50` | Maximum concurrent job instances |
| `SCHEDULER_TIMEZONE` | `UTC` | Timezone for cron triggers |

#### Analysis Configuration

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `MAX_CONCURRENT_EXECUTIONS` | `10` | Maximum concurrent template executions |
| `EXECUTION_TIMEOUT_SECONDS` | `300` | Timeout for single template execution (5 minutes) |
| `BASELINE_CALCULATION_WINDOW` | `30d` | Time window for baseline calculation |

#### Anomaly Detection Configuration

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `ANOMALY_DETECTION_ENABLED` | `true` | Enable anomaly detection system |
| `ANOMALY_Z_SCORE_THRESHOLD` | `3.0` | Z-score threshold for anomaly classification |
| `ANOMALY_MIN_SAMPLES` | `30` | Minimum samples required before anomaly detection |

#### Alerting Configuration

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `ALERTING_ENABLED` | `true` | Enable alert system |
| `ALERT_EMAIL_ENABLED` | `false` | Enable email notifications |
| `ALERT_WEBHOOK_ENABLED` | `false` | Enable webhook notifications |
| `ALERT_WEBHOOK_URL` | (empty) | Webhook URL for alert notifications |

#### External Services

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `AUTH_SERVICE_URL` | `http://localhost:8000` | Auth service URL for JWT validation |
| `CONTENT_ANALYSIS_SERVICE_URL` | `http://localhost:8002` | Content analysis service URL |
| `RESEARCH_SERVICE_URL` | `http://localhost:8003` | Research service URL |
| `FEED_SERVICE_URL` | `http://localhost:8001` | Feed service URL |

#### JWT Configuration

