### Adding Custom Templates

1. Create a new YAML file in the appropriate category directory:
   ```bash
   touch app/templates/my_category/my_template.yaml
   ```

2. Define template structure following the schema above

3. Reload templates:
   ```bash
   curl -X POST http://localhost:8004/api/v1/templates/reload \
     -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>"
   ```

