## Deployment

### Docker Deployment

**Development:**

```bash
# Build image
docker build -f Dockerfile.dev -t osint-service:dev .

# Run container
docker run -d \
  --name osint-service \
  -p 8004:8004 \
  -e DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@postgres:5432/db \
  -e REDIS_URL=redis://:pass@redis:6379/0 \
  -e JWT_SECRET_KEY=your-secret-key \
  osint-service:dev
